   By Bill McCarthy • September 28, 2021                     Instagram posts   stated on September 25, 2021 an Instagram post:         \"Maricopa County official purged machine records before audit started.\"             By Bill McCarthy • September 28, 2021                     Tweets   stated on August 30, 2021 tweets:         A video shows the “Taliban hanging someone from a helicopter.”             By Bill McCarthy • August 31, 2021                      Joe Rogan   stated on August 20, 2021 a podcast episode:         The mRNA COVID-19 vaccines are “really gene therapy.”             By Bill McCarthy • August 31, 2021              $123,000 turkey? Viral photo of pricey Target turkey is several years old, shows pricing error                   Mary Miller   stated on October 23, 2021 in a tweet:         The migrant caravan from Tapachula, Mexico “is the population of Minneapolis.”             By Kiannah Sepeda-Miller • October 31, 2021                     Instagram posts   stated on October 27, 2021 in an Instagram post:         Blood “starts to clot in a minute or two” after a Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine injection.             By Tom Kertscher • October 29, 2021                     Hal Turner Radio Show   stated on October 27, 2021 in an article:         “Japan drops vax rollout”             By Monique Curet • October 29, 2021                     Facebook posts   stated on October 27, 2021 in a Facebook post:         Virginia voters are being turned away from polling locations because they were told they already requested absentee ballots when they haven’t.             By Samantha Putterman • October 29, 2021                     Viral image   stated on October 24, 2021 in a Facebook post:         In-N-Out cups say “F--- Joe Biden.”              By Ciara O&#39;Rourke • October 29, 2021                     Viral image   stated on October 27, 2021 in an Instagram post:         Says a CNN headline said, “In And Out is the fast food of white supremacists.”             By Ciara O&#39;Rourke • October 29, 2021                      Facebook posts   stated on October 20, 2021 in a Facebook post:         “Atlanta just lost 75% of its police force”             By Andy Nguyen • October 29, 2021                     Facebook posts   stated on October 27, 2021 in a Facebook post:         “Trump is in White House! He promises to lock up Hillary!”             By Ciara O&#39;Rourke • October 29, 2021                     Thom Tillis   stated on October 26, 2021 in a tweet:         \"Gas in North Carolina increased 14 cents per gallon this past week, the highest in the nation.\"             By Paul Specht • October 29, 2021                     Viral image   stated on October 27, 2021 in an Instagram post:         \"There is no such thing as a booster. There is a failed product that is sometimes used again in hopes of a different outcome.”             By Tom Kertscher • October 29, 2021          Load more          Support independent fact-checking.\r\n Become a member!   In a world of wild talk and fake news, help us stand up for the facts. </pc>\n\n  Sign me up                        Offices  District of Columbia  \r\n  1100 Connecticut Ave. NW\r\n Suite 1300B  \r\n Washington, DC  20036\n\n  Florida \r\n  801 3rd St. S  \r\n St. Petersburg, FL  33701 \r\n 727-821-9494         People      All People     Joe Biden     Kamala Harris     Charles Schumer     Mitch McConnell     Bernie Sanders     Nancy Pelosi     Donald Trump          State Editions    California Florida Illinois Iowa Missouri New York North Carolina Pennsylvania Texas Virginia West Virginia Vermont Wisconsin Michigan        About Us      Our Process      Our Staff     Who pays for PolitiFact?     Advertise with Us     Corrections and Updates        RSS Feeds      Recent Articles and Fact-checks     Recent Fact-checks         Suggest a Fact-check           Follow us                   The Facts Newsletter         Sign up         Terms &amp; Conditions   Privacy Policy   Copyright   ©All R