(46, '                 NASA to launch \"Armageddon\"-style mission to deliberately crash into an asteroids moon and test \"planetary defense\" - CBS News     ', 'https://www.cbsnews.com/news/nasa-dart-mission-crash-asteroid-moon-planetary-defense/', '                                                                                                                                                       Election Day 2021                        Free CBS News App                        Stream CBSN Live                        Sign Up For Newsletters                        The New Pro-Gun Generation                        COVID Pandemic                        CBS Village                                                                                                                                                     News                                                                                                                                                           US                                                                                                                                                World                                                                                                                                                Politics                                                                                                                                                Entertainment                                                                                                                                                Health                                                                                                                                                MoneyWatch                                                                                                                                                CBS Village                                                                                                       